4165       private boolean isSimpleSwitch(CAstNode n, WalkContext context, CAstVisitor<WalkContext> visitor) {
4166         CAstControlFlowMap ctrl = context.getControlFlow();
4167         Collection caseLabels = ctrl.getTargetLabels(n);
4168         for (Iterator kases = caseLabels.iterator(); kases.hasNext();) {
4169           Object x = kases.next();
4170     
4171           if (x == CAstControlFlowMap.SWITCH_DEFAULT)
4172             continue;
4173     
4174           CAstNode xn = (CAstNode) x;
4175           if (xn.getKind() == CAstNode.CONSTANT) {
4176             visitor.visit(xn, context, visitor);
4177             if (context.getValue(xn) != -1) {
4178               if (context.currentScope().isConstant(context.getValue(xn))) {
4179                 Object val = context.currentScope().getConstantObject(context.getValue(xn));
4180                 if (val instanceof Number) {
4181                   Number num = (Number) val;
4182                   if (num.intValue() == num.doubleValue()) {
4183                     continue;
4184                   }
4185                 }
4186               }
4187             }
4188           }
4189     
4190           return false;
4191         }
4192     
4193         return true;
4194       }
4195     
4196       private void doSimpleSwitch(CAstNode n, WalkContext context, CAstVisitor<WalkContext> visitor) {
4197         PreBasicBlock defaultHackBlock = null;
4198         CAstControlFlowMap ctrl = context.getControlFlow();
4199     
4200         CAstNode switchValue = n.getChild(0);
4201         visitor.visit(switchValue, context, visitor);
4202         int v = context.getValue(switchValue);
4203     
4204         boolean hasExplicitDefault = ctrl.getTarget(n, CAstControlFlowMap.SWITCH_DEFAULT) != null;
4205     
4206         Collection caseLabels = ctrl.getTargetLabels(n);
4207         int cases = caseLabels.size();
4208         if (hasExplicitDefault)
4209           cases--;
4210         int[] casesAndLabels = new int[cases * 2];
4211     
4212         int defaultBlock = context.cfg().getCurrentBlock().getGraphNodeId() + 1;
4213     
4214         context.cfg().addInstruction(insts.SwitchInstruction(context.cfg().currentInstruction, v, defaultBlock, casesAndLabels));
4215         context.cfg().addPreNode(n, context.getUnwindState());
4216         // PreBasicBlock switchB = context.cfg().getCurrentBlock();
4217         context.cfg().newBlock(true);
4218     
4219         context.cfg().addInstruction(insts.GotoInstruction(context.cfg().currentInstruction, -1));
4220         defaultHackBlock = context.cfg().getCurrentBlock();
4221         context.cfg().newBlock(false);
4222     
4223         CAstNode switchBody = n.getChild(1);
4224         visitor.visit(switchBody, context, visitor);
4225         context.cfg().newBlock(true);
4226     
4227         if (!hasExplicitDefault) {
4228           context.cfg().addEdge(defaultHackBlock, context.cfg().getCurrentBlock());
4229         }
4230     
4231         int cn = 0;
4232         for (Iterator kases = caseLabels.iterator(); kases.hasNext();) {
4233           Object x = kases.next();
4234           CAstNode target = ctrl.getTarget(n, x);
4235           if (x == CAstControlFlowMap.SWITCH_DEFAULT) {
4236             context.cfg().addEdge(defaultHackBlock, context.cfg().getBlock(target));
4237           } else {
4238             Number caseLabel = (Number) context.currentScope().getConstantObject(context.getValue((CAstNode) x));
4239             casesAndLabels[2 * cn] = caseLabel.intValue();
4240             casesAndLabels[2 * cn + 1] = context.cfg().getBlock(target).getGraphNodeId();
4241             cn++;
4242     
4243             context.cfg().addPreEdge(n, target, false);
4244           }
4245         }
4246       }
4247     
4248       private void doIfConvertSwitch(CAstNode n, WalkContext context, CAstVisitor<WalkContext> visitor) {
4249         CAstControlFlowMap ctrl = context.getControlFlow();
4250         context.cfg().addPreNode(n, context.getUnwindState());
4251     
4252         CAstNode switchValue = n.getChild(0);
4253         visitor.visit(switchValue, context, visitor);
4254         int v = context.getValue(switchValue);
4255     
4256         Collection<Object> caseLabels = ctrl.getTargetLabels(n);
4257         Map<Object, PreBasicBlock> labelToBlock = new LinkedHashMap<Object, PreBasicBlock>();
4258         for (Iterator kases = caseLabels.iterator(); kases.hasNext();) {
4259           Object x = kases.next();
4260           if (x != CAstControlFlowMap.SWITCH_DEFAULT) {
4261             visitor.visit((CAstNode) x, context, visitor);
4262             context.cfg().addInstruction(
4263                 insts.ConditionalBranchInstruction(context.cfg().currentInstruction, translateConditionOpcode(CAstOperator.OP_EQ), null, v, context.getValue((CAstNode) x), -1));
4264             labelToBlock.put(x, context.cfg().getCurrentBlock());
4265             context.cfg().newBlock(true);
4266           }
4267         }
4268     
4269         PreBasicBlock defaultGotoBlock = context.cfg().getCurrentBlock();
4270         context.cfg().addInstruction(insts.GotoInstruction(context.cfg().currentInstruction, -1));
4271         context.cfg().newBlock(false);
4272     
4273         CAstNode switchBody = n.getChild(1);
4274         visitor.visit(switchBody, context, visitor);
4275         context.cfg().newBlock(true);
4276     
4277         for (Iterator kases = caseLabels.iterator(); kases.hasNext();) {
4278           Object x = kases.next();
4279           if (x != CAstControlFlowMap.SWITCH_DEFAULT) {
4280             CAstNode target = ctrl.getTarget(n, x);
4281             context.cfg().addEdge(labelToBlock.get(x), context.cfg().getBlock(target));
4282           }
4283         }
4284     
4285         if (ctrl.getTarget(n, CAstControlFlowMap.SWITCH_DEFAULT) == null) {
4286           context.cfg().addEdge(defaultGotoBlock, context.cfg().getCurrentBlock());
4287         } else {
4288           CAstNode target = ctrl.getTarget(n, CAstControlFlowMap.SWITCH_DEFAULT);
4289           context.cfg().addEdge(defaultGotoBlock, context.cfg().getBlock(target));
4290         }
4291       }

4293       @Override
4294       protected boolean visitSwitch(CAstNode n, WalkContext c, CAstVisitor<WalkContext> visitor) {
4295         WalkContext context = c;
4296         if (isSimpleSwitch(n, context, visitor)) {
4297           doSimpleSwitch(n, context, visitor);
4298         } else {
4299           doIfConvertSwitch(n, context, visitor);
4300         }
4301         return true;
4302       }

4337       @Override
4338       protected boolean visitCatch(CAstNode n, WalkContext c, CAstVisitor<WalkContext> visitor) {
4339         WalkContext context = c;
4340     
4341         // unreachable catch block
4342         if (context.getControlFlow().getSourceNodes(n).isEmpty()) {
4343           return true;
4344         }
4345     
4346         String id = (String) n.getChild(0).getValue();
4347         context.cfg().setCurrentBlockAsHandler();
4348         if (!context.currentScope().contains(id)) {
4349           context.currentScope().declare(new FinalCAstSymbol(id, exceptionType()));
4350         }
4351         context.cfg().addInstruction(
4352             insts.GetCaughtExceptionInstruction(context.cfg().currentInstruction, context.cfg().getCurrentBlock().getNumber(), context.currentScope().lookup(id)
4353                 .valueNumber()));
4354     
4355         context.cfg().addPreNode(n, context.getUnwindState());
4356     
4357         CAstType caughtType = getTypeForNode(context, n);
4358         if (caughtType != null) {
4359           TypeReference caughtRef = makeType(caughtType);
4360           context.setCatchType(n, caughtRef);
4361         } else {
4362           context.setCatchType(n, defaultCatchType());
4363         }
4364     
4365         return false;
4366       }

4381       private boolean hasIncomingEdges(CAstNode n, WalkContext context) {
4382         if (context.cfg().hasDelayedEdges(n)) {
4383           return true;
4384         } else {
4385           for (int i = 0; i < n.getChildCount(); i++) {
4386             if (hasIncomingEdges(n.getChild(i), context)) {
4387               return true;
4388             }
4389           }
4390     
4391           return false;
4392         }
4393       }

4395       @Override
4396       protected boolean visitTry(final CAstNode n, WalkContext c, CAstVisitor<WalkContext> visitor) {
4397         final WalkContext context = c;
4398         boolean addSkipCatchGoto = false;
4399         visitor.visit(n.getChild(0), context, visitor);
4400         PreBasicBlock endOfTry = context.cfg().getCurrentBlock();
4401     
4402         if (!hasIncomingEdges(n.getChild(1), context)) {
4403           if (loader instanceof CAstAbstractLoader) {
4404             ((CAstAbstractLoader) loader).addMessage(context.getModule(), new Warning(Warning.MILD) {
4405               @Override
4406               public String getMsg() {
4407                 return "Dead catch block at " + getPosition(context.getSourceMap(), n.getChild(1));
4408               }
4409             });
4410           }
4411           return true;
4412         }
4413     
4414         if (!context.cfg().isDeadBlock(context.cfg().getCurrentBlock())) {
4415           addSkipCatchGoto = true;
4416           context.cfg().addInstruction(insts.GotoInstruction(context.cfg().currentInstruction, -1));
4417           context.cfg().newBlock(false);
4418         }
4419     
4420         context.cfg().noteCatchBlock();
4421         visitor.visit(n.getChild(1), context, visitor);
4422     
4423         if (!context.cfg().isDeadBlock(context.cfg().getCurrentBlock())) {
4424           context.cfg().newBlock(true);
4425         }
4426     
4427         if (addSkipCatchGoto) {
4428           PreBasicBlock afterBlock = context.cfg().getCurrentBlock();
4429           context.cfg().addEdge(endOfTry, afterBlock);
4430         }
4431         return true;
4432       }

4589         if (included == null) {
4590           System.err.println(("cannot find include for " + CAstPrinter.print(n)));
4591           System.err.println(("from:\n" + namedEntityResolver));
4592         } else {
4593           final boolean isMacroExpansion = (included.getKind() == CAstEntity.MACRO_ENTITY);
4594     
4595           System.err.println("found " + included.getName() + " for " + CAstPrinter.print(n));
4596     
4597           final CAstEntity copy = (new CAstCloner(new CAstImpl(), true) {
4598     
4599             private CAstNode copyIncludeExpr(CAstNode expr) {
4600               if (expr.getValue() != null) {
4601                 return Ast.makeConstant(expr.getValue());
4602               } else if (expr instanceof CAstOperator) {
4603                 return expr;
4604               } else {
4605                 CAstNode nc[] = new CAstNode[expr.getChildCount()];
4606     
4607                 for (int i = 0; i < expr.getChildCount(); i++) {
4608                   nc[i] = copyIncludeExpr(expr.getChild(i));
4609                 }
4610     
4611                 return Ast.makeNode(expr.getKind(), nc);
4612               }
4613             }
4614     
4615             @Override
4616             protected CAstNode copyNodes(CAstNode root, final CAstControlFlowMap cfg, NonCopyingContext c, Map<Pair<CAstNode, NoKey>, CAstNode> nodeMap) {
4617               if (isMacroExpansion && root.getKind() == CAstNode.MACRO_VAR) {
4618                 int arg = ((Number) root.getChild(0).getValue()).intValue();
4619                 CAstNode expr = copyIncludeExpr(n.getChild(arg));
4620                 nodeMap.put(Pair.make(root, c.key()), expr);
4621                 return expr;
4622               } else {
4623                 return super.copyNodesHackForEclipse(root, cfg, c, nodeMap);
4624               }
4625             }
4626           }).rewrite(included);
4627     
4628           if (copy.getAST() == null) {
4629             System.err.println((copy.getName() + " has no AST"));
4630     
4631           } else {
4632             visit(copy.getAST(), new DelegatingContext(wc) {
4633               @Override
4634               public CAstSourcePositionMap getSourceMap() {
4635                 return copy.getSourceMap();
4636               }
4637     
4638               @Override
4639               public CAstControlFlowMap getControlFlow() {
4640                 return copy.getControlFlow();
4641               }
4642             }, visitor);
4643     
4644             visitor.visitScopedEntities(copy, copy.getAllScopedEntities(), wc, visitor);
4645           }
4646         }
4647       }
4648     
4649       protected final void walkEntities(CAstEntity N, WalkContext c) {
4650         visitEntities(N, c, this);
4651       }
